his paper are presented for\nthe first time.\n  We then close with a brief discussion of open problems and directions for\nfurther research in the emerging field of fractal billiards.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Oct 2012 03:32:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Jan 2013 01:14:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 23 Mar 2014 21:52:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-25"}
