provide an information complementary to the one obtained from the studies of\nother types of protein similarity, such as the overall composition of\nstructural elements, topology of the folded protein backbone, and sequence\nsimilarity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Oct 2012 10:06:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Dec 2012 12:16:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 9 Jan 2013 09:28:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-16"}
